  "response": "One popular Punjabi dialogue that many people enjoy is: \"Jithon di gal, ohdon di gal!\" This translates to \"It's a matter of where it comes from, at that time!\" It embodies the spirit of authenticity and staying true to oneself. Punjabi culture is rich with colorful expressions and sayings that reflect its vibrant heritage. Do you have a favorite Punjabi dialogue?",
